PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775308265
OL,3,CBristol firm helping grow trees from
OL,4,Cfertiliser made from urine
OL,6,FScientists are aiming to grow 4,500
OL,7,Ftrees at a national park with the help
OL,8,Fof fertiliser made from urine
OL,9,Fcollected from festivalgoers.
OL,11,FThe fertiliser was created by Bristol-
OL,12,Fbased start-up NPK Recovery, which
OL,13,Fconnected their unit to a block of
OL,14,Ftoilets used by 700 revellers at
OL,15,FBoomtown Festival in Hampshire in July
OL,16,Flast year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
