OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775308265
OL,3,CBristol firm helping grow trees from
OL,4,Cfertiliser made from urine
OL,6,FThis urine was turned into 540 litres
OL,7,Fof fertiliser during the 2025 event,
OL,8,Fand will now be used to grow native
OL,9,Ftrees such as beech on the edge of
OL,10,FBannau Brycheiniog, also known as the
OL,11,FBrecon Beacons, in Wales.
OL,13,FUrine from other sources will also be
OL,14,Fused during the three-year project,
OL,15,Fwhich has been backed by a grant from
OL,16,Fthe Forestry Commission.
OL,18,FOn Thursday morning (April 2) a Scots
OL,19,Fpine seed was planted at the site to
OL,20,Fmark the launch of the initiative.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775308265
OL,3,CBristol firm helping grow trees from
OL,4,Cfertiliser made from urine
OL,6,FLucy Bell-Reeves, co-founder of NPK
OL,7,FRecovery, said trials had shown their
OL,8,Ffertiliser was as effective as
OL,9,Fcommonly used alternatives.
OL,11,FThis project will be the first time it
OL,12,Fhas been trialled on trees.
OL,14,F"Using a waste product to grow trees
OL,15,Fis a circular solution that can
OL,16,Frevitalise our struggling native
OL,17,Fspecies," she said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775308265
OL,3,CBristol firm helping grow trees from
OL,4,Cfertiliser made from urine
OL,6,F"We need to stop flushing crop and
OL,7,Ftree-growing nutrients down the loo
OL,8,Fand start using them to increase our
OL,9,Ffertiliser security.
OL,11,F"After all, we're not about to run out
OL,12,Fof urine any time soon.
OL,14,F"I love the idea that by the end of
OL,15,Fthis three-year project, revellers
OL,16,Fwill have created a fledgling Welsh
OL,17,Fforest, which could flourish for
OL,18,Fhundreds of years."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
