PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775308265
OL,3,CBristol firm helping grow trees from
OL,4,Cfertiliser made from urine
OL,6,FIn April last year, the company
OL,7,Fcollected 1,000 litres of urine from
OL,8,Fwomen's urinals at the TCS London
OL,9,FMarathon which was processed into
OL,10,Ffertiliser.
OL,12,FIt uses bacteria to recover nitrogen
OL,13,Fand other naturally occurring
OL,14,Fnutrients from the urine, creating a
OL,15,Fliquid odour-free fertiliser.
OL,17,FNPK Recovery has a mobile laboratory
OL,18,Fthat it brings to events, enabling the
OL,19,Furine to be processed into fertiliser
OL,20,Fat source.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
