PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775308265
OL,3,CBristol firm helping grow trees from
OL,4,Cfertiliser made from urine
OL,6,FAs part of the Welsh project, the
OL,7,Fcompany has partnered with charity
OL,8,FStump up for Trees which was co-
OL,9,Ffounded by author and cyclist Rob Penn.
OL,11,FOver the past five years, the charity
OL,12,Fhas planted more than 500,000 trees in
OL,13,Fthe area ` halfway towards their
OL,14,Ftarget of one millions trees to
OL,15,Fdeliver landscape restoration.
OL,17,F"We are very excited to be involved in
OL,18,Fthis ground-breaking project, which
OL,19,Fhas implications for the future of
OL,20,Fsustainable forestry," he said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
