OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775308265
OL,3,CBristol firm helping grow trees from
OL,4,Cfertiliser made from urine
OL,6,F"As a small charity, collaboration is
OL,7,Fessential and we are chuffed to be
OL,8,Fworking with NPK Recovery, who are
OL,9,Fbringing innovation to an area of
OL,10,Findustry that needs it."
OL,12,FThe project received a #435,627
OL,13,FForestry Commission grant, awarded via
OL,14,Fthe Tree Production Innovation Fund.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]
